➜爷青回！万万男团重聚，叫兽易小星新片《沐浴之王》定档1211
http://www.sohu.com/a/433185509_359734	35663
<p>“怀念万合兄弟”、“怀念叫兽易小星”的帖子几乎是豆瓣月经贴👇万万没想到，这一次“万万男团”重聚SZD！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201120/55efdddaec104cd1b423a784c1300a62.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201120/58df0623fb954866a98cd22601ac4d43.png" max-width="600" /></p>
